Experiment 8:  
Write a shell script to check whether a given number is even or odd

experiment.sh
#!/bin/bash
echo "Enter a number: "
read num
if [ $((num % 2)) -eq 0 ]
then
    echo "$num is Even!!"
else
    echo "$num is Odd!"
fi

